      "value": "<p><em><strong>Consular:</strong> 2nd level</em></p>\n<p>You gain the ability to twist your powers to suit your needs. When you cast a force power, you can expend additional force points to modify the power. You gain two Force-Empowered Casting options, located at the end of the class description, and you learn more at higher levels, as shown in the Force-Empowered Casting Options of the cnosular table.</p>\n<p>You can use only one Force-Empowered Casting option on a power when you cast it, unless otherwise noted.</p>",
